c: 4
v: 6
t: "Zivavanyeni iinkedama zide zifikelele ebudaleni bokuba zitshate; ukuba ke nizifumanise ukuba zinengqiqo epheleleyo, zikhululeni iimpahla zazo, kodwa ningazidli ngokuzidyakraza, nigxabhagxabhisa kuba nisoyikisela ukuba ziza kukhula kananjalo lowo usisityebi (kwabo bangabagcini bazo) makangathathi ntlawulo, kodwa ukuba ulihlwempu, makazithabathele okuselungelweni ngobulungisa (ngokusebenza kwakhe) ke kaloku xa nizikhululela iimpahla zazo thabathani amangqina abekhona phambi kwazo; kananjalo uAllâh Wanele Eyedwa ukuba Afake abantu embuzweni"